Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ask thee, Father, to forgive us\Nour sins and grant us eternal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we leave this world, may we\Ngo peacefully into the arms of our Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We offer this prayer to our savior,\Nthe Lord Jesus Christ. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:02:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As her soul departs from this world,\Nmay she find eternal peace in the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:33.18,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 9\NAlone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. You've been dragging\Nyour feet, and now you're running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that the dinner tonight is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you say, but If you had gotten ready\Nearlier, I wouldn't have to be nagging you-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will that girl be at the dinner party as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Miss Campbell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. You're her escort, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duty is duty. I'll just have to put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I want my father to accept Emma,\NI can't show any sign of weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try. I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Emma is a weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant. Stop nitpicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And stop being so familar,\Nyou should call her "Miss Emma"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if both families encourage the match,\Nit's up to the couple themselves in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And therein lies the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't guess the feelings of a woman in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Eleanor, I can't pull any tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be fashionable to have a tiny\Nwaist, but this is very bad for your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a trick to opening the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to push and lift at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's small and old, but it will have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The front door was open. That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kitchen will take a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked my mates to help out. They'll\Nget rid of anything you don't need next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. You've done so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't told him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Jones boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The funeral may be over, but you\Nshould still tell him, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize you don't have to wear\Na maid uniform anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just force of habit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you were here a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, could I have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Campbell! Mr. William Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Melville, thank you for your invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a beautiful home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eleanor, you're more beautiful\Nevery time I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same to you dear aunt,\Nyou're as beautiful as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, even your words have\Nthe grace of a true lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I hope you don't mind escorting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jones suggested that I come,\Nand I couldn't help but comply...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it was impudent of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I'm grateful, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seemed a little out of sorts recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, I am delighted\Nthat you've gathered here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you will enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, to your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is sea turtle soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even cooked, a sea turtle still ends up\Nswimming in water, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lobster and sole cooked in an orange sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything tastes so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is puree of ptarmigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must remember to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm forgetting my manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm forgetting them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 43 and 44 have gone up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the garnish finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add the final touches, please!\NYes, Cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add the final touches, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add the final touches, please!\NAll right, move on to the sauce then, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, move on to the sauce then, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the roast duck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, Cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:10:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect. I did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, take it up.\NYou're fired if you drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up with the trimmings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't handle wine to begin with,\Nyou get used to it the more you drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I drank, I made a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with people who loved to drink, so l\Ncouldn't refuse when they offered me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Port wine, Hock, Claret, Sherry,\Nthere was even Madeira, I think....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the ladies retired to the next room,\NI trod on the hem of the lady next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have yet to make a single mistake, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was worried\Nbefore I left the house tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me not to disgrace the\Ntraditions of our family...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother is always talking about it,\Ntradition this, tradition that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tradition is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, tradition is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's something that has been\Nhanded down through many generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I despise the idea of upholding\Ntradition simply for the sake of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just being stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't mean to criticize your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just speaking of the topic in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you'll have to\Nsearch for another house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't much at all, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's ready. This is the final dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the guests said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems very satisfied.\NEven the mistress was praising you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go, being modest again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, we're not finished yet!\NWe still have to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you start daydreaming\Nand break a valuable plate,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be packing your bags\Ncome tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, it's delightful to dine\Nwith a young couple like yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Young love is clearer than crystal,\Nmore vibrant than gardens in June."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not... not really the case here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invited the young lady to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I would be happy\Nif love were to blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, "One sees the elegance of\Nthe rose in the bud." Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the salon is ready,\Nso the ladies can now retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the gentlemen\Nwish to smoke their cigars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so full. I wish I could take my corset off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um... is William always at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he likes round games.\NPerhaps I should ask him next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my brother is so unpredictable.\NHe doesn't make for very good company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! I really enjoy talking with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... ifWilliam already\Nhas someone that he likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear! Just listen to me babble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This biscuit tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Eleanor, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Eleanor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm fine, didn't l?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,William!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my father's rudeness earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's something\NI have to tell you, Eleanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truthfully, I don't know\Nwhether I should tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it may make you uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, to be silent any longer\Nwould be dishonest to my...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not feeling very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I had too much wine,\NI'm still not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I must excuse myself for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I'll escort you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie, call the carriage, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home alone, tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible that after all this work,\Nwe never get to eat the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do get to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean the leftovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. They're the\Naristocrats, and we're the cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the gap between us is\Nwider than the London Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be cooks, but when the flavors we create\Nmove the hearts of the nobles, in that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we become equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say that? "lf love would blossom."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only spoke of my personal wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same thing! You talk\Nas if it's already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you oppose me,\Nmy feelings won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not some childish whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to consider my responsibilities\Nto the Jones family, and I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of this talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?\NDo you want something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:09.00,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode:\NMissing One Another
